<title>ạyd ạlmsyḥ mmdwdẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạyd ạlmsyḥ mmdwdẗ wbqwẗ gẖyr mḥdwdẗ

[V2]
 mḥfwẓ bạyd ạlrb wlạ ạḥml ywm ạlhm

[V3]
 wklạmẗ jwẗ ạqlb wʿạạysẖ fyy ḥmạh ạldm

[V4]
 ạlqrạr- lyly mḍỷ wạydyn ạlhy btsẖddny ṭwl ạlṭryq nʿmẗ ạlhy btsndnyy

[V5]
 2- ạyd ạlmsyḥ btqwmny mn ạy ḍʿf btrfʿny

[V6]
 bqdạsẗ qlb wfkr ạrjʿ wạʿysẖ fy ạydyẗ

[V7]
 ạbn ạlmsyḥ ạlḥr ạlnwr dymạ yḥyẗ

[V8]
 3- ạyd ạlmsyḥ btʿlmny wfy ạlṭryq bttẖbtny

[V9]
 ạly wʿdny wwʿdẗ ạly ạnqḍạʾ ạldhr

[V10]
 rwḥẗ ạlqdws wḥbẗ ḥạmyny mn ạy sẖr

[V11]
 4- ạyd ạlmsyḥ btkạfỷny ṭwl ạlṭryq btrfʿny

[V12]
 kẖạdm ạlhy ạlḥy fy kl ḥyạty mʿạẗ ạlly wʿdny wjạy hạʿysẖ dymạ wyạẗ</lyrics>
</song>